text: The 1902 Navy Midshipmen football team served as the team of the United States Naval Academy in the 1902 college football season. In their second season under head coach Art Hillebrand, the Midshipmen got a 2–7–1 record and were beat by opponents by a total score of 99 to 35. ==Schedule== ==References== Category:1900s in sports Category:1900s in the United States
